{"tid":744728,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國新星好波又有善心　麥巴比為國效力不收報酬","createTime":"2018-07-16T07:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T07:17:37.000Z","uid":113626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9ddf258b996b6b895bfd8cbb68eae3ba5c84cb70","tid":744728,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"法國《隊報》報道，年僅19歲的基利安麥巴比經過深思熟慮，認為代表國家隊比賽不需要酬勞，應該將金錢放在慈善用途上，故此決定捐出所有從法國足總所得來的獎金。<br />\n<br />\n麥巴比一直支持為病童提供參加體育運動機會的團體Premiers de Cord&eacute;e，據指他早在4月已許下承諾，捐出今夏參加世界盃所獲得的獎金。若然法國隊能夠一搔20年之癢，一舉奪冠，每名球員可各分得30萬歐元獎金（約274萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢條友好似會將所有世界盃收益捐哂出去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bbee60f5a420282209cf63096d2decd438336d","tid":744728,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"30萬對佢黎講係一星期人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37b9180636e9ba76a91136fa092f60f01495836","tid":744728,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71bbee60f5a420282209cf63096d2decd438336d","tid":744728,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"30萬對佢黎講係一星期人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"除左冠軍好似每場出場果個錢都會捐埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8085fa3d5ff0ecc289f7827ec1b573d1aa50b087","tid":744728,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"呢單抵讚既<br />\n唔好話對佢黎講算多定少<br />\n始終都係幫到人呀"},{"pid":"dd364b5a9a697c6baa484320c08847de03561e4e","tid":744728,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:17:03.000Z","msg":"職業球員邊會至在國家隊d錢呀<br />\n<br />\n佢地依加係球會一星期搵都唔少錢啦<br />\n<br />\n真係為錢咩?<br />\n<br />\n為名為利為夢想先落力踢國家隊<br />\n<br />\n<br